OL,3,CMurder suspect due in court as inquest
OL,4,Cinto Ann Widdecombe's death opens
OL,6,FA 28-year-old man is due in court
OL,7,Fcharged with the murder of Ann
OL,8,FWiddecombe, as an inquest heard her
OL,9,Fcause of death is yet to be
OL,10,Festablished.
OL,12,FJoshua Kerry, from Rotherham, South
OL,13,FYorkshire, arrived at Westminster
OL,14,FMagistrates' Court on Tuesday, charged
OL,15,Fwith the murder of the former MP and
OL,16,FReform UK spokeswoman.
OL,18,FIt comes as an inquest into her death
OL,19,Fat Exeter County Hall heard she was
OL,20,Ffound at her home in Devon with
OL,21,F"visible injuries".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
