OL,3,CMurder suspect due in court as inquest
OL,4,Cinto Ann Widdecombe's death opens
OL,6,FHer cause of death is yet to be
OL,7,Festablished, Senior Coroner Phillip
OL,8,FSpinney told the inquest.
OL,10,FIn a five-minute hearing, Mr Spinney
OL,11,Fsaid: "Concerns were raised that she
OL,12,Fwas uncontactable.
OL,14,F"An employee was asked to conduct a
OL,15,Fwelfare check. Miss Widdecombe was
OL,16,Ffound unresponsive with visible
OL,17,Finjuries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784677676
OL,3,CMurder suspect due in court as inquest
OL,4,Cinto Ann Widdecombe's death opens
OL,6,F"The emergency services were called
OL,7,Fand she was sadly declared deceased at
OL,8,Fthe scene. The precise cause of death
OL,9,Fis yet to be established."
OL,11,FMr Spinney told the court this has
OL,12,Fbeen an "intensive and complex
OL,13,Finvestigation" and that he would
OL,14,Fsuspend the inquest until the
OL,15,Fconclusion of criminal proceedings.
OL,17,FKerry, who has been remanded into
OL,18,Fcustody, was first arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of murder on July 11, two
OL,20,Fdays after the 78-year-old was found
OL,21,Fdead at her home in Devon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
