OL,3,CMurder suspect due in court as inquest
OL,4,Cinto Ann Widdecombe's death opens
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FTwo days after he was arrested for
OL,12,Fmurder, Kerry was additionally
OL,13,Farrested on suspicion of the
OL,14,Fcommission, preparation or instigation
OL,15,Fof acts of terrorism, but he has not
OL,16,Fbeen charged with this offence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
